"Wright":
"Yikes! No matter how many times I come here,
I still find these heights terrifying. But I won't
let anything stop me this time!"

"Let's get started. Oh, but let's avoid the
really high places, shall we?"

"うぅ、何度来ても
生きた心地のしない高さですね……
でも、今日こそは頑張らなければ！"

"それでは行きましょう！
あ、でもあんまり高いところは
勘弁してくださいね……！"
